theorem.name: sumList_app

text.english: Interaction between \(\texttt{sumList}\) and \(\texttt{app}\), i.e. \begin{multline} \forall l_1,l_2 \in L_\mathbb{N} . \\ \texttt{sumList}(\texttt{app}(l_1,l_2)) = \texttt{susList}(l_1) + \texttt{sumList}(l_2) \end{multline}
text.italiano: Interazione fra \(\texttt{sumList}\) e \(\texttt{app}\), i.e. \begin{multline} \forall l_1,l_2 \in L_\mathbb{N} . \\ \texttt{sumList}(\texttt{app}(l_1,l_2)) = \texttt{susList}(l_1) + \texttt{sumList}(l_2) \end{multline}

theorem.coq:
Theorem sumList_app: forall l1 l2 : listn , sumList (app l1 l2)  = sumList l1 + sumList l2.
Proof.
Admitted.
